snippet.title: The Box by Amber Rose || SlutBox || A Rant-y Review
snippet.description:
#amberrose #Cherrybomb #New

Hello loves!  I had SO much fun filming this one...seriously! Mood was up, I’d had a nap, blood pressure was normal...anyway, what do you guys think of this one?  I did not leave a link for you to try it, but if you’re truly interested in the box, let me know and I’ll drop the link...prepare yourself for some...interesting unboxing fun!

I’m working to shorten my videos so it’s easily digestible, with the exception of my vlogs, which can be up to an hour long.

Links for all the stuff - transparency included!!

Vellabox: As far as I can tell - I get nothing, and you can choose a subscription!
https://www.vellabox.com/subscribe/

Boxycharm: I get 500 charms for each one of you that use my link
https://www.boxycharm.com/refer/Audra-RCCTLJUT

Allure Beauty Box:What I get varies - typically free products
http://fbuy.me/v/heyweirdoa

Vine! Oh! - You get $10 off when you make a purchase and I get $10 towards the shop
http://vineoh.refr.cc/audrah

Stitch Fix: You get $25.00 and so do I! https://www.stitchfix.com/referral/6510672?sod=w&som=c&g=w

Scentbird: You get a free perfume and so do I!
https://www.scentbird.com/r/d/audrahoffman

Splendies: Who doesn’t need new panties?
https://www.splendies.com/refer/Audra-NEJNHIAH
Ipsy: I literally have no idea what happens with this one.
https://www.ipsy.com/new?cid=ppage_ref&sid=link&refer=xls0b

Birchbox: I receive $10 in Birchbox points, whatever that means
https://www.birchbox.com/invite/294cn

Nadine West: You get free shipping and a $10 credit, I get a $10 credit.
http://fbuy.me/m9JYu

Barkbox: It looks like I possibly earn a free box - it doesn’t say what you get for joining..
http://www.barkbox.com/r/sc/KSI398DS4P

JustFab: I get $15 towards purchase and 50 reward points, you’ll get a sweet deal on your first purchase
https://www.justfab.com/invite/47281763

Shoedazzle: I get $20 towards a purchase, you receive 75% off your first order!
www.shoedazzle.com/invite/104684636/

Intro & Outro: GOLETS - Slaves

Instagram: @audra.at.home www.instagram.com/audra.at.home/
SnapChat: ARowdygirl
Twitter: @heyweirdoa
Facebook: Audra Rowdygirl
Influenster: Audra Rowdygirl

As always, never spend time building someone up who only wants to tear you down.

Blessed Be!
XOXO,

Audra

*Disclaimer: Unless otherwise stated, I am not sponsored by any of the companies or products mentioned in this video.  All opinions are my own and are for entertainment purposes only.*
